getContentMetrics(bytes32).details: Return the staking and earning information of a StakedContent ID

params._stakedContentId: The ID of the staked content

getContentMetrics(bytes32).return: the network base ion amount staked for this contentthe primordial ion amount staked for this contentthe primordial weighted multiplier of the staked contentthe total earning from staking this contentthe total earning from hosting this contentthe total The AO earning of this content

getEarningMetrics(bytes32).details: Return the earning information of a StakedContent ID

setAOSettingAddress(address).details: The AO sets AO Setting address

setAOTreasuryAddress(address).details: The AO sets AO Treasury address

setSettingTAOId(address).details: The AO sets setting TAO ID

params._settingTAOId: The new setting TAO ID to set

setWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist `_account` address to transact on behalf of others

stakeAOContent(uint256,uint256,bytes8,ui.details: Stake `_networkIntegerAmount` + `_networkFractionAmount` of network ion in `_denomination` and/or `_primordialAmount` primordial ion for an AO Content

params._baseChallenge: The base challenge string (PUBLIC KEY) of the content
params._contentDatKey: The dat key of the content
params._denomination: The denomination of the network ion, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.
params._encChallenge: The encrypted challenge string (PUBLIC KEY) of the content unique to the host
params._metadataDatKey: The dat key of the content's metadata
params._networkFractionAmount: The fraction amount of network ion to stake
params._networkIntegerAmount: The integer amount of network ion to stake
params._primordialAmount: The amount of primordial ion to stake
params._profitPercentage: The percentage of profit the stake owner's media will charge

stakeCreativeCommonsContent(uint256,uint.details: Stake `_networkIntegerAmount` + `_networkFractionAmount` of network ion in `_denomination` and/or `_primordialAmount` primordial ion for a Creative Commons Content

params._baseChallenge: The base challenge string (PUBLIC KEY) of the content
params._contentDatKey: The dat key of the content
params._denomination: The denomination of the network ion, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.
params._encChallenge: The encrypted challenge string (PUBLIC KEY) of the content unique to the host
params._metadataDatKey: The dat key of the content's metadata
params._networkFractionAmount: The fraction amount of network ion to stake
params._networkIntegerAmount: The integer amount of network on to stake
params._primordialAmount: The amount of primordial ion to stake

stakeTAOContent(uint256,uint256,bytes8,u.details: Stake `_networkIntegerAmount` + `_networkFractionAmount` of network ion in `_denomination` and/or `_primordialAmount` primordial ion for a T(AO) Content

params._baseChallenge: The base challenge string (PUBLIC KEY) of the content
params._contentDatKey: The dat key of the content
params._denomination: The denomination of the network ion, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.
params._encChallenge: The encrypted challenge string (PUBLIC KEY) of the content unique to the host
params._metadataDatKey: The dat key of the content's metadata
params._networkFractionAmount: The fraction amount of network ion to stake
params._networkIntegerAmount: The integer amount of network ion to stake
params._primordialAmount: The amount of primordial ion to stake
params._taoId: The TAO (TAO) ID for this content (if this is a T(AO) Content)

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership of The AO to new address

params._theAO: The new address to be transferred

devdoc.title: AOContentFactory * The purpose of this contract is to allow content creator to stake network AO ions and/or primordial AO+ ions on his/her content
